name: 'Don't Let it Swallow you Whole' (orb01, LotteZ 2021)
description: These is inspired by gig posters from psychedelic rock bands from the 60s and vintage comic books. Some of these orbs are derivatives of artwork that I have designed for internationally touring bands between 2016-2021. Follow me on Twitter: @LotteZ13 , on instagram.com/lottezproductions and www.lottez.com
